{"id": "2310", "post": "<div class=\"post-2310 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-onepoundwebhosting-co-uk tag-uk tag-xen\" id=\"post-2310\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/onepoundwebhosting-6-30quarter-128mb-xen-vps-in-uk/\" rel=\"bookmark\">OnePoundWebHosting \u2013 \u00a36.30/Quarter 128MB Xen VPS in UK</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/onepoundwebhosting-co-uk/\" rel=\"tag\">onepoundwebhosting.co.uk</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/uk/\" rel=\"tag\">uk</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> December 24, 2011 @ 12:47 pm, by LowEndAdmin</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://www.onepoundwebhosting.co.uk/\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/images/onepoundwebhosting.jpg\" class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"OnePoundWebHosting\"></a> Stuart, MD of <a href=\"http://www.onepoundwebhosting.co.uk/\"><b>OnePoundWebHosting</b></a>, sent me some special discount for the LowEndBox readers a few days before <a href=\"/blog/running-out-of-time-and-i-am-taking-a-break/\">my break</a>. However as the offer is still valid I think it\u2019s not too late to post it. They are offering <b>30% off</b> recurring discount on their <a href=\"http://www.onepoundwebhosting.co.uk/pvvpshosting.php\">Xen PV</a> or <a href=\"http://www.onepoundwebhosting.co.uk/hvmvpshosting.php\">Xen HVM</a> VPS hosting plans when you use coupon code <b>LOWEND30</b>, valid until 19 January 2012. Their cheapest plan \u201cPV-128\u201d would be <b>\u00a36.30/Quarter</b> (~USD$3.27/month) after the discount. <a href=\"https://www.onepoundwebhosting.co.uk/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=2amp;promocode=LOWEND30\">Direct sign up link here</a>.</p><ul><li>128MB memory/128MB swap</li><li>10GB storage</li><li>250GB/month data transfer</li><li>4x vCPU cores</li><li>Xen/SolusVM</li></ul><p>Corresponding <a href=\"http://www.webhostingtalk.com/showthread.php?t=1109346\">WHT offer here</a> (different code, same discount). They have servers with <a href=\"http://www.serverhouse.co.uk/\">ServerHouse</a> in UK (test IP: 195.49.147.100). OnePoundWebHosting is a registered UK company since 2006 (company number: 05886975). IRC is explicitly forbidden in ToS. Sounds like a strong team \u2014 but it could still be a one man show, like how <a href=\"http://www.webhostingtalk.com/showthread.php?t=575854\">this review almost 5 years ago</a> has described.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fonepoundwebhosting-6-30quarter-128mb-xen-vps-in-uk%2F&amp;t=OnePoundWebHosting%20-%20%C2%A36.30%2FQuarter%20128MB%20Xen%20VPS%20in%20UK\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=OnePoundWebHosting%20-%20%C2%A36.30%2FQuarter%20128MB%20Xen%20VPS%20in%20UK&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fonepoundwebhosting-6-30qu